    <pb facs="liv_000073_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><cb n="1"/>
<lb/><p><add place="marginleft" hand="#U"><hi rend="vertical">22</hi></add> <choice><sic>slept</sic><corr>Slept</corr></choice> on bank of the
<lb/>most southern branch of
<lb/>the <placeName><geogName type="river">Monikazi</geogName></placeName> &amp; on
<lb/><space unit="chars" extent="3"/><date from="1871" to="1873">9<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi></date> after <measure>two hours</measure>
<lb/>threading its very winding
<lb/>deep channel came to a
<lb/>village where our men
<lb/>crossed it &amp; sent after
<lb/>them = we are all tired
<lb/>by the rushes and <term type="plant">vegetation</term></p>
<lb/><space dim="vertical" rend="line" extent="4"/>
<lb/><figure><head>Gandochite chief</head><figDesc>May of rivers and dates traveled through land.</figDesc></figure> <!-- Adrian, not sure if the head for this is the name of the chief, or some geog locational name? HB -->
<lb/>
<lb/><cb n="2"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><date from="1871" to="1873">7<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi></date> <choice><sic>slept</sic><corr>Slept</corr></choice> on an <term type="insect">ant</term>hill
<lb/>Went on <measure>2 hours</measure> then
<lb/>came to a broad shallow
<lb/>bench on right of the
<lb/><placeName><geogName type="river">Monikazi <choice><abbr>R.</abbr><expan>River</expan></choice></geogName></placeName> had to
<lb/>unload canoes &amp; haul
<lb/>each over into <placeName><geogName type="river">Monikaze</geogName></placeName>
<lb/>which has a thick fringe
<lb/>of <term type="plant">Papyrus</term> - then
<lb/>hearing voices &amp; a drum
<lb/>went East &amp; lost our <unclear cert="low">way</unclear>
<lb/>in stiff grassy prairies
<lb/>which could scarcely be
<lb/>got through = <unclear cert="low">in</unclear> <measure>5 hours</measure>
<lb/>slept on an <term type="insect">ant</term>hill
<lb/>a <term type="animal">lion</term> wandering &amp; roaring
<lb/>in the waste of waters</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><date from="1871" to="1873">8<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi></date> <choice><sic>send</sic><corr>Send</corr></choice> a canoe to
<lb/><choice><abbr>vil</abbr><expan>village</expan></choice> where voices come
<lb/>from for information -
<lb/><term type="plant">Papyrus plants</term> 8 feet
<lb/>long <choice><orig>Â¼</orig><reg>1/4</reg></choice> in diameter - crown
<lb/>3 feet across horizontally ==
<lb/>got two <term type="occupation">guides</term> but the
<lb/>water <measure><measure>about 15 inches</measure> in
<lb/><add place="marginleft"><figure><figDesc>Calculations spanning the next 5 lines in margin.</figDesc></figure></add> spots and <measure>thigh deep</measure></measure> in
<lb/>others caused constant
<lb/>dragging of the large canoe
<lb/>through rushes <space unit="chars" extent="2"/><term type="plant">Papyrus</term>
<lb/><foreign xml:lang="und"><term type="plant_foodstuff">arum</term></foreign> = <term type="plant_foodstuff">wild rice</term> &amp; stiff
<lb/>grasses aquatic = <measure>5 Hours <choice><abbr>E &amp; S.</abbr><expan>East and South</expan></choice></measure></p>
<lb/>
<lb/><cb n="3"/>
<lb/><figure><figDesc>Calculations.</figDesc></figure>



